ASP.NET Core Web API .NET 8

Reference: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBTe6uHJS_Y&list=PL82C6-O4XrHfrGOCPmKmwTO7M0avXyQKc

Last video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cSnoAGHKVus&list=PL82C6-O4XrHfrGOCPmKmwTO7M0avXyQKc&index=4

1. In a new folder run the following command in terminal - dotnet new webapi -o api
2. run - dotnet watch run
3. remove boilerplate code in program.cs between app.UseHttpsRedirection(); and app.Run(); and the record after app.Run();
4. ctrl shift p -> search NuGet Gallery -> EFC SqlServer / Tools / Design
5. create models
6. create ApplicationDBContext
7. create db in SSMS
8. add ConnectionString to appsettings.json
9. run - dotnet ef migrations add Init (first run -> dotnet tool install --global dotnet-ef --version 8.0.x)
10. run - dotnet ef database update
